        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nMaven tests with api & pap, as did they're respective CSITs, as well as drools-apps CSIT.\n\nChanges to models were:\n2.3.3: fixed bug in A&AI actor; never released\n2.3.4: released with no additional changes\n2.3.5: fix to CDS simulator and TOSCA default policy\n\nDoesn't seem worth generating a whole round of updates just to check these out for a few hours, thus releasing 2.3.5 and bumping the other repos straight to 2.3.5 once that's done.",
